Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========Pre=========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========OP=========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.22,0:00:05.73,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:15.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}僕らの願いが届くまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:24.26,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}大事なものまた一つ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.88,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}モノクロの空へと消える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:35.67,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隠したキズ冷たく震え
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:40.05,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分の居場所を探す
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:47.86,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}常識に従うこの世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:52.58,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}どうしようもできないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:56.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}壊していきたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:01:04.33,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}閉ざしたココロ叫んでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:11.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみ連鎖の中で僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:17.42,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}自分さえも見失いそうになって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.10,0:01:21.35,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}曖昧な答えはイラナイ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:27.86,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}確かな今　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.22,0:00:05.73,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲伤的连锁之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:15.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在我们的愿望实现之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:24.26,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}又一件珍贵的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.88,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}消失在黑白的空中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:35.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}隐藏的伤痕在发冷颤抖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:40.05,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去找寻我的容身之处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:47.86,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在这个遵循常识的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:52.58,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想打破无可救药的桎梏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:56.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}按自己的意志自由生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:01:04.33,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}封闭的心灵正发出呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:11.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲伤的连锁之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.88,0:01:17.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我们几乎快要迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.10,0:01:21.35,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}不需要暧昧的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.45,0:01:27.86,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}只需去追寻真切的现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======TEXT=======
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:39.36,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,400)}果てなく続く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.82,0:01:58.83,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,400)}光は強く明日を照らす　胸の…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.26,0:02:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 路过听到声音而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.51,0:02:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才唱得是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念远方故乡的达鲁库斯歌谣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是达鲁库斯的人偶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 想把它作为精灵节的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.57,0:02:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 给谁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你想得出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵节送什么礼物 我们又不是孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.67,0:02:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向平日里照顾自己的人和身边人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表达谢意 是件好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说 送给谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算送给哥哥的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:02:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.44,0:03:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁鲁和兰蒂格瑞丝也能看到同样的月亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 抱歉说些奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛鲁贝利海岸？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次奉命执行的作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是歼灭那里的帝国军防御阵地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为歼灭敌人基地 必须穿过空旷的海岸地带
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人布阵于峭壁间的山坡上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两旁有坚固的碉堡群
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于无处藏身 进攻方将处于压倒性劣势
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自始至终暴露在敌人炮火下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.71,0:03:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有迹象表明敌人打算从那里攻打加利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.78,0:03:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择此时进攻的意义究竟何在…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达蒙将军打算让第七小队充当先锋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正规军呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会视义勇军的作战进展情况而定…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我去向队员说明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这是队长的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巩特尔少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉声叹气会影响士气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巩特尔少尉 刚才把补缺目录放在你桌上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请过目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹别扭？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…你怎么会来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你看看也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近博格宰相和达蒙将军接触频繁 听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达蒙将军方面有可疑举动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来已经发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上个月在兰蒂格瑞丝城的事 我还记得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博格宰相 军功章 达蒙将军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上能让人联想到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃利特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.11,0:05:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿我的忠告是多此一举
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 埃利特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉不是艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.72,0:05:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.22,0:06:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听帕罗特女士说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们成了别人的眼中钉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…不是军队的机密文件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么机密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本入不了他们的法眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就借来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加利亚北部战线出现神秘的青色发光现象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正规军第五中队损失惨重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起什么玛鲁贝利 他们应该多关心这些才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上就是作战情况说明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.79,0:06:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 精灵节也要去打仗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天不能外出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是全家团聚的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争不会顾及这些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请忘记精灵节吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 全都是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 维尔金总是动不动就道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长能这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 得到勋章得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗茜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,义勇军不自量力去接受什么勋章 所以被人盯上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.99,0:07:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说 罗茜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.04,0:07:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是对方说要颁发的 队长有什么过错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长大人好出风头招致反感 使我们成为众矢之的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗茜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.76,0:07:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是达蒙将军用心险恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 队长没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能向帝国和达蒙屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅也高兴点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气会生皱纹的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗茜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要感谢我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为罗茜小姐的话 哥哥才没有成为恶人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是说真心话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样行不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种小队里 到时候怎么死的都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让任何人死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃米尔 画啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第七小队的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是精灵节
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想空着手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼物？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我送给维尔金？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…毕竟是队长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.89,0:09:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是两码事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夫妻吵架？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我可辛苦了 又没时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顾不了什么精灵节
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法尔迪奥也会安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔金也是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要烤焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烫伤了吗 好严重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须马上处理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 法尔迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上回也烤焦了一锅面包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又烫伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没脸自称大师级别了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多泡一会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这人伤好得特别快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.99,0:10:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点担心柴火 得去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过会见 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.02,0:11:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成是在做精灵节的礼物？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能替我保密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不想告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽顾着自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哥哥的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在维尔金面前太撒娇了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是得认清自己的身份与他相处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅怎么看待哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看待？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说了那种话 但我认为他是个好队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥看起来称职 是因为他一心想做好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从父亲死后 哥哥时常显得不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅 请不要讨厌哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下 打开看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.62,0:13:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快收下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵节快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵节快乐 法尔迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快好了 看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽西娅的父母也是这种体质吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 我从小在孤儿院长大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是那块救了我的Ragnite吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.62,0:13:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你重新收下它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你的 因为是精灵节
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你的那份送出去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要送哦 说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.14,0:14:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有海流的影响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎整天都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整天…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:14:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这里有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有东西想给哥哥看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟雾弹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过改良 延长了在空中滞留的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那种风势下 不知有多大效果…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛鲁贝利海岸看似整日暴露在强风中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上朝夕各有一小时 处于无风状态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是最好的攻击时机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟雾弹发射的同时全员突击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由Edelweiss号摧毁敌人碉堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抵达暗礁地带后 由步兵继续突入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会这么顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深更半夜偷偷摸摸 原来在做这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗  我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.32,0:15:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 考虑到不能保证完成…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没敢告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没能完成 我们就会变成交叉火力下的靶子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗茜 少说几句
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该感谢伊莎拉才对 而不是挖苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗茜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精灵节的礼物 虽然迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.54,0:16:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达鲁库斯自古相传的护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能逢凶化吉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要给我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送给模范哥哥不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 罗茜是突击时的先锋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:17:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它保佑了罗茜 也就保佑了第七小队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张嘴比你哥哥甜多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎拉 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 烟雾弹发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员突击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算借烟雾掩护接近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别怕 敌人看不见我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.22,0:17:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟雾有增无减
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听声音 朝敌人炮火声的方向射击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们无法行动反而不利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出动士兵 主动迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 有人在也说一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1点方向敌人据点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突击时拜托掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗茜 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.09,0:19:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是为了拾它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就被爆头了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗茜 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗茜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托别在人耳边扯着嗓门喊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家加把油 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗茜和伊莎拉在这里待命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的人跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.55,0:19:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别退缩 给我不停地开火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 基地受到加利亚军两面夹击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退 给我撤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来还算顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.77,0:20:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗茜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤势不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.33,0:20:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏这个护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======ED=======
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:47.31,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}悲しすぎる瞳が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:53.98,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}この空を映す
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:22:02.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}掛ける言葉がわからずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:08.22,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただ　星を数えた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.74,0:22:13.94,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}孤独で居る世界は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:20.72,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}得意なはずだと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:27.23,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}振りかえる日々　あぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.68,0:22:33.66,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}探していた　きみをひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:40.30,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}もしもいま許されるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:46.99,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}きみのことだけ想うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.15,0:22:54.88,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}忘れたくない悲しみならば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.34,0:23:02.42,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}ただそれが　それだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:08.62,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)\be1}そう  ひとつの願い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:47.31,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}太过悲伤的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:53.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}映照出这片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.35,0:22:02.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}不知该说什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:08.22,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)\be1}只默默数着星星
